is to make everyone happy

00:23:07.679 --> 00:23:09.639 align:middle
with your singing.

00:23:09.723 --> 00:23:12.392 align:middle
Singing? For everyone?

00:23:12.475 --> 00:23:13.518 align:middle
[MATSUMOTO]
You got it!

00:23:13.601 --> 00:23:16.646 align:middle
Now then, everybody's
waiting for you.

00:23:21.985 --> 00:23:23.528 align:middle
[MATSUMOTO]
